window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Even though Asterios was quite uncertain about the lavish gift he had received from the king, he accepted the responsibility of leading the village of Glimmervale. Things definitely weren't easy in the beginning, but with proper teamwork and help from their friends and relatives, he and the girls managed to fit right in, additionally solving the issues bothering the town and capturing the hearts of people by making sure that everyone felt safe. Now that things are finally calming down, Asterios and his companions can continue their journey and depart into Bryn's realm without any worries...</p> <p>The vast but majorly unhabitable realm of floating, metal fortresses awaits them with all the challenges hiding in the breathtaking ARKs. Will they be able to easily locate the Descending Spire without spending months on their search? Are they going to tackle its retrieval alone or alongside new allies? Is anyone even going to be willing to aid them on such a dangerous mission? And finally, does it hold any answers to their ever-growing questions?</p> <p>Since Red had directly instructed them to seek the Spire, they are certainly hoping for the best.</p>"; 
